title: ENDURANCE CALORIE SHRED | 40 MIN Treadmill Workout!
description:
Today we are crushing a 40 Min Endurance Calorie Shred Tread workout! Let's get out there to crush it!

Join this channel to get access to perks and support the channel!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJumOlRn9C592ijW9sUC2Hg/join

40 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com
Merch: https://www.ibxrunning.com/store
IBX Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ibxrunning/
Rachael's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bedopefitness/

00:00 - Intro
00:40 - Warm Up
03:40 - Workout!
39:10 - Cool Down!

comments: I've been doing all your videos to get back into running postpartum. This one might just be my favorite! You totally made me believe I could finish and I did!

January 31, 2025: thank you for this workout. I had a miscarriage this week and I’m walking thru grief and depression. I came to the gym this morning to workout but didn’t want to workout alone. Search treadmill workout on YouTube and this came up for me. It was exactly what I needed. So funny and encouraging. I’m so grateful for you!  I finished the workout and I feel so good. Thank you!
60 minute runs would be amazing! Your workouts are the highlight of my days. I push myself harder working out with you!
Did this run yesterday 11-20-24. 3.21 miles 724 calories burned. Mind you I’m 6’3” 250lbs. I enjoy your run workouts.
LOVE you Rachel, you are the reason I run on a treadmill at all!!!!!! Bring on a 60 minute workout !!!
